Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502705852\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"42\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2401e1e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zotCTF2kebByIao1mukeoCXNY3JU0WuJBsy2jtgbt4REff8WQwWR4oQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkt9qmz1wnl\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkt9qnr205\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">One More Thing</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkt3pm91lqb\">Groq并不是唯一一家在AI浪潮中崛起的芯片初创公司。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkt3pm9lqj\">英特尔已明确表示有意向收购AI芯片初创公司SambaNova，目前处于深入谈判阶段，甚至已签署了不具约束力的意向书。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkt3pm918lh\">英特尔现任CEO陈立武曾担任SambaNova的执行董事长，其创投公司华登国际也是SambaNova的早期投资者之一。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100373922\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5046296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;width:100%;text-align:start;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"276\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35fd2413&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYicUhk5aAGtCIpBvYubpRPEvA05guIm919p7kKvIV5bbhJUlEjLlvIfErAc6Zk4qybUMBMefcYP8IHDWqFbM90w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D6\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkt3pm9ux2\">另一家明星企业Cerebras原本计划今年上市，却在10月撤回了IPO申请，转而完成了一轮超过10亿美元的融资。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkt3pm91jd9\">Cerebras的发言人表示，公司仍希望尽快上市，但并未透露撤回IPO的具体原因。又或者Cerebras的结局也是被一家巨头收购也说不定。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100373924\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.6824074074074075\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;width:100%;text-align:start;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"373\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7c6134c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYicUhk5aAGtCIpBvYubpRPEvA05guIm911iaqOaibcO21K0O8rDERJAN6PEAKCBRmTK2iaGdk4BFOVgb1z8EqYiaSmg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D7\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkt3pm9yxs\">Groq、SambaNova和Cerebras最初都是以GPU颠覆者的形态登场。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkt3pm914xy\">当巨头开始用资本手段吸收潜在的颠覆者，留给其他玩家的窗口期或许正在收窄。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkta2qmy6i\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkta2qdnou\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">参考链接：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkta2qd13lc\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">[1]<a href=\"https://groq.com/newsroom/groq-and-nvidia-enter-non-exclusive-inference-technology-licensing-agreement-to-accelerate-ai-inference-at-global-scale\" target=\"_blank\">https://groq.com/newsroom/groq-and-nvidia-enter-non-exclusive-inference-technology-licensing-agreement-to-accelerate-ai-inference-at-global-scale</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkta2qd23cb\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">[2]<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2025/12/24/nvidia-buying-ai-chip-startup-groq-for-about-20-billion-biggest-deal.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2025/12/24/nvidia-buying-ai-chip-startup-groq-for-about-20-billion-biggest-deal.html</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "英伟达通过 200 亿美元的“人才收购”方式，获得 Groq 的技术授权并吸纳其核心团队，剑指 AI 推理市场，此举是科技巨头规避反垄断并快速获取顶尖 AI 人才和技术的典型案例。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "英伟达通过 200 亿美元的“人才收购”方式，获得 Groq 的技术授权并吸纳其核心团队，剑指 AI 推理市场，此举是科技巨头规避反垄断并快速获取顶尖 AI 人才和技术的典型案例。",
  "summary": "文章报道了英伟达以 200 亿美元与 AI 芯片初创公司 Groq 达成的一项“技术许可协议”，而非此前盛传的收购。该事件的核心是英伟达通过重金获取 Groq 的技术授权，并吸纳了包括创始人 Jonathan Ross 在内的“TPU 核心班底”，旨在强化其在 AI 推理市场的布局。Groq 以其低延迟、高能效的 LPU（语言处理单元）在 AI 推理领域独树一帜，其创始人曾是谷歌 TPU 的核心研发者。文章还列举了近年来科技巨头通过“人才收购”（Acqui-hire）模式规避反垄断审查、快速获取顶尖 AI 人才和技术的多个案例，如微软收购 Inflection 核心团队、谷歌挖角 Character.AI 等，并提及了其他 AI 芯片初创公司如 SambaNova 和 Cerebras 的动向，指出巨头资本整合下留给颠覆者的窗口期正在收窄。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "英伟达以 200 亿美元通过技术许可协议形式，获得 Groq 技术并吸纳其核心团队",
      "explanation": "这笔交易并非传统意义的收购，而是通过高额技术授权并引入关键人才，规避了潜在的反垄断审查，使英伟达能快速获得 Groq 在 AI 推理领域的领先技术和人才。"
    },
    {
      "point": "交易战略意图在于强化英伟达在 AI 推理市场的主导地位",
